# React / Next.js in this repo

Before editing matched files, read:

1. `.agents/skills/ponytail/SKILL.md` — minimal diff, no over-engineering
2. `.agents/skills/vercel-react-best-practices/SKILL.md` — performance patterns

For visual changes, also read `.agents/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md` and align with `CONTEXT.md` (light minimal, TH default).

- Prefer Server Components; add `"use client"` only when needed (i18n, interactivity)
- Content in `src/content/site.ts`, not hardcoded in components
- Keep bundle lean — no new deps without ponytail justification
